      "question": "Why was the forget gate an important addition to the original LSTM idea?",
      "stem_format": "plain_text",
      "choices_format": "plain_text",
      "choices": [
        "Because pure accumulation without forgetting becomes dysfunctional on long sequences",
        "Because it makes the model exactly equivalent to a CNN",
