        "Because it removes the need for any hidden state"
      ],
      "answer_index": 0,
      "explanation": "A purely additive memory that only keeps accumulating content eventually becomes overloaded. The forget gate lets the model clear or reduce stale information so memory remains useful over long sequences.",
